PN,40501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782400703
OL,3,CInfected water scandal was a result of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' from South West
OL,5,CWater
OL,7,FThe infected water scandal in Brixham
OL,8,Fwhich left hundreds of people unwell
OL,9,Fcould have been avoided if South West
OL,10,FWater had followed the proper
OL,11,Fprocedures, according to a new report.
OL,13,FIn 2024, 537 people fell ill and 10
OL,14,Fwere hospitalised after the water
OL,15,Fsupply was contaminated with the
OL,16,Fparasite cryptosporidium.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
