OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782400703
OL,3,CInfected water scandal was a result of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' from South West
OL,5,CWater
OL,7,FAround 16,000 homes and businesses in
OL,8,FBrixham, Kingswear and Paignton - a
OL,9,Fpopulation of almost 39,000 - were
OL,10,Ftold to boil their water and the
OL,11,Fnotice was not lifted until July 2024.
OL,13,FEarlier this month, South West Water
OL,14,Fwas fined #1.9 million after admitting
OL,15,Fsupplying water that was unfit for
OL,16,Fhuman consumption.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782400703
OL,3,CInfected water scandal was a result of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' from South West
OL,5,CWater
OL,7,FNow, a report from the Drinking Water
OL,8,FInspectorate has found the outbreak
OL,9,Fwas a "serious and avoidable public
OL,10,Fhealth incident" which arose from
OL,11,F"systemic failures in asset
OL,12,Finspection, governance and risk
OL,13,Fmanagement".
OL,15,FMeanwhile, reports suggest Susan Davy,
OL,16,Fformer chief executive of South West
OL,17,FWater, has accepted a bonus of
OL,18,F#270,000 for 2024-25, along with an
OL,19,F#87,000 bonus for 2025-26.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782400703
OL,3,CInfected water scandal was a result of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' from South West
OL,5,CWater
OL,7,FThat comes on top of a salary and
OL,8,Fbenefits package that took her
OL,9,Fearnings above #1 million in 2024-25,
OL,10,Fonce pensions and share allocations
OL,11,Fwere included, according to the Daily
OL,12,FTelegraph.
OL,14,FThe Drinking Water Inspectorate report
OL,15,Ffound the parasite entered the water
OL,16,Fsystem from animal faeces through a
OL,17,Ffaulty air valve in a field.
OL,19,FThe DWI said the valve had not been
OL,20,Finspected since 2011, despite several
OL,21,Frecommendations to do so.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782400703
OL,3,CInfected water scandal was a result of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' from South West
OL,5,CWater
OL,7,FThe report says: "The company failed
OL,8,Fto implement known and documented
OL,9,Fcontrol measures.
OL,11,F"The event had a significant impact on
OL,12,Fconsumers and communities. There were
OL,13,Fconfirmed and probable cases of
OL,14,Fcryptosporidiosis associated with the
OL,15,Foutbreak, widespread consumer concern,
OL,16,Fdisruption to households, impacts on
OL,17,Flocal businesses and effects on school
OL,18,Fattendance and education.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782400703
OL,3,CInfected water scandal was a result of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' from South West
OL,5,CWater
OL,7,F"The duration of the restrictions for
OL,8,Fsome consumers materially increased
OL,9,Fthe scale of that impact.
OL,11,F"The company failed to follow prior
OL,12,Fregulatory warnings on air valves and
OL,13,Finspection of high-risk water users."
OL,15,FThe DWI sent out questionnaires to
OL,16,Fmore than 300 people following the
OL,17,Foutbreak.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782400703
OL,3,CInfected water scandal was a result of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' from South West
OL,5,CWater
OL,7,FInspectors found that the company's
OL,8,Fadvice to continue using the water as
OL,9,Fnormal, despite people falling ill,
OL,10,Fled to anger among customers.
OL,12,F"Water companies should give careful
OL,13,Fconsideration to the appropriateness
OL,14,Fof their messaging at the outset of an
OL,15,Finvestigation into a potential public
OL,16,Fhealth outbreak," the report says.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782400703
OL,3,CInfected water scandal was a result of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' from South West
OL,5,CWater
OL,7,F"Also, where a phased or sequential
OL,8,Fapproach is used to lift boil water
OL,9,Fnotices, water companies should
OL,10,Fensure, prior to lifting any notice,
OL,11,Fthat their systems and processes
OL,12,Faccurately identify the relevant
OL,13,Fproperties so that correct advice is
OL,14,Fprovided to consumers."
OL,16,FDavid Harris, managing director of
OL,17,Fwater services for South West Water,
OL,18,Fsaid: "We have co-operated fully with
OL,19,Fthe Drinking Water Inspectorate
OL,20,Fthroughout its investigations.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782400703
OL,3,CInfected water scandal was a result of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' from South West
OL,5,CWater
OL,7,F"We apologise again to our customers
OL,8,Fwho were impacted and have always
OL,9,Ftaken full responsibility for the
OL,10,Fwater that was supplied.
OL,12,F"Hundreds of our skilled colleagues
OL,13,Fworked tirelessly to fix the issues
OL,14,Ffaced during the incident. We will
OL,15,Fcontinue to work every day to rebuild
OL,16,Ftrust and our relationships with the
OL,17,Fcommunities who were impacted by this
OL,18,Fextremely rare event in 2024.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782400703
OL,3,CInfected water scandal was a result of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' from South West
OL,5,CWater
OL,7,F"That started during the incident
OL,8,Fitself where the prosecution
OL,9,Facknowledged today in court that South
OL,10,FWest Water went above and beyond with
OL,11,Frespect to the provision of bottled
OL,12,Fwater and more generally made no
OL,13,Fcriticism of our incident response.
OL,15,F'We have also developed smart air
OL,16,Fvalves - an industry leading step up -
OL,17,Fand changed our processes to ensure
OL,18,Fearlier precautionary boil water
OL,19,Fnotices can be issued where necessary."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782400703
OL,3,CInfected water scandal was a result of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' from South West
OL,5,CWater
OL,7,FKeith Haslett, chief executive officer
OL,8,Fof Pennon Group which owns SWW, added:
OL,9,F"While I have only been CEO of this
OL,10,Fbusiness for a few weeks, it is very
OL,11,Fclear that we must learn lessons from
OL,12,Fthis incident and work hard to
OL,13,Fcontinue to rebuild trust with the
OL,14,Fcustomers and communities we serve,
OL,15,Fboth in Brixham and beyond.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782400703
OL,3,CInfected water scandal was a result of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' from South West
OL,5,CWater
OL,7,F"I am already focussed on driving
OL,8,Fimprovement in the way we operate, how
OL,9,Fwe communicate and support our
OL,10,Fcustomers during operational
OL,11,Fincidents, and driving a step change
OL,12,Fin our performance for our customers
OL,13,Fand the environment."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
